---
title: Vegan Sweet Chili Tofu Bowls with Zesty Rice, Cabbage, Carrots & Peanuts
description: Don’t get us wrong, plates are great—but there’s just something ‘bout a bowl! This one’s brimming with plant-powered goodness, thanks to crumbled tofu mixed with sautéed cabbage, carrots, and onion. Everything’s coated in a trio of tangy sauces—soy sauce, sweet soy glaze, and Thai chili sauce—then served over zesty lime rice and topped with peanuts and cilantro. Textured, flavorful, filling and vegan? This bowl’s gone above and beyond.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-sweet-chili-tofu-bowls-32869c02.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/vegan-sweet-chili-tofu-bowls-63aa8e653ff7f0537e0422a3-3128289d.pdf
author: HelloFresh
